BT /F2 14.5 Tf 0.13 0.15 0.2 rg 54 736 Td (3.  Overview) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 0.13 0.15 0.2 rg 54 708 Td (AI-Argus-Harness maps, analyzes, verifies and reports security exposure across modern enterprise) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 0.13 0.15 0.2 rg 54 695 Td (environments: external attack surface, cloud, identity, Kubernetes, applications/APIs, SaaS and the) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 0.13 0.15 0.2 rg 54 682 Td (software supply chain. It is evidence-first: deterministic scanners produce structured evidence and AI) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 0.13 0.15 0.2 rg 54 669 Td (only reasons over that evidence, which sharply reduces hallucinations and keeps runs reproducible and) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 0.13 0.15 0.2 rg 54 656 Td (audit-ready.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 0.1 0.2 0.34 rg 54 631 Td (Core principle) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 0.13 0.15 0.2 rg 54 611 Td (AI is an evidence interpreter, never an evidence creator. A finding is only promoted to enterprise) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 0.13 0.15 0.2 rg 54 598 Td (reporting when it carries: asset, evidence, identity path \(for high/critical\), impact, confidence,) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 0.13 0.15 0.2 rg 54 585 Td (remediation and owner. Anything incomplete is routed to human review \(or dropped in strict mode\).) Tj ET
